From: Joseph Magly <1159087+jmagly@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Apr 2026 03:55:33 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 25/25] fix(m147): finalize post-rebase API drift fixes
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

These are the build fixes mentioned in carbonyl rebase commit
(58e50bd) that were applied to the working tree but never committed.
Committing now so patches.sh save captures them into the canonical
patch set.

Fixes land-in-one-commit for simplicity; can be squashed into the
original rebase history later if desired:

- viz software_output_device_proxy.cc: ResourceSizes::MaybeSizeInBytes
  → SinglePlaneFormat::MaybeEstimatedSizeInBytes (M147 API)
- browser_interface_binders.cc: Mojo BinderMap::Add signature change
  (BindRepeating → template helper)
- headless/BUILD.gn: remove phantom //carbonyl/src/browser:carbonyl
  dep (target doesn't exist; was leftover from earlier rebase)
- headless_browser_impl.cc: resolve merge conflict + add
  navigation_controller.h; PlatformSetWebContentsBounds →
  SetWebContentsBounds; zoom_controller include
- headless_screen.cc: remove duplicate ~HeadlessScreen; fix brace
  placement for IsHeadless()
- headless_web_contents_impl.h: using WebContentsObserver::
  OnVisibilityChanged to resolve virtual overload hiding
- text_decoration_painter.cc: (void)skip_ink suppression
- font.cc: remove dead Font::DrawText(TextRun) overloads
  (CachingWordShaper/ShapeResultBuffer removed in M147)
- paint_artifact_compositor.cc: remove orphan debug dump function
